Bathroom has both toilet and urinal. 
There is no one "on duty," and people doing their laundry generally mind their own beeswax, so no one should bother you.

name: Public restroom

go to the customer service desk in the back right corner of the store, then through the big doorway on the right then it's the little door on the left.
there's one single-stall locking room.

No code needed
